#: src/unsaved.asm:55
msgid "Save changes?"
msgstr "是否保存更改?"

#: src/unsaved.asm:56
msgid "This document has unsaved changes. If you close without saving, those changes will be lost."
msgstr "此文档包含未保存的更改。如果不保存就关闭，这些更改将会丢失。"

